有些东西在下坠，有些东西在上升，或许都是幽灵，或许都是虚无的思绪.Translation: Some things are falling, some things are rising; perhaps they are all ghosts, perhaps they are thoughts of nothingness.

它们如同你梦境中的一般的欢迎你.Translation: They welcome you just like in your dreams.

可这里只有失望和混乱....Translation: But here there is only disappointment and chaos...
